et3.java.application

Class Network

  • java.lang.Object
    • et3.java.application.Network

  • public class Network
extends java.lang.Object
    Network class represents all the objects known in the system. The user interacts in the main() with it each time he wants to operate (adding, consulting, removing) on a document, library or that kind of objects. A Network object encapsulates collections of libraries, documents, authors, series and users.
